race.comment: MORE RAIN (1) produced a speedy 29.73 when filling a minor placing over 515m at this track last start. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. JONESY REVENGE (3) ran good time (25.55) when placing two back at Maitland but missed the frame latest in a Grade 5 at Maitland. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. SAHARA PEARL (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.06) in a Grade 5 at this track. In the mix. SHE'S BLISSFUL (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
